dmill-project`\n- Script path: `/home/user/windmill-project/f/scripts/user_info.ts`\n- Metadata path: `/home/user/windmill-project/f/scripts/user_info.script.yaml`\n- The `display` field format must be: `[${id}] ${name} (active)` or `[${id}] ${name} (inactive)`\n\n## Integrations\n\nNone."}}
